Class RemoveTypeFileSmall

  • java.lang.Object
    • cn.trinea.android.common.service.impl.RemoveTypeFileSmall
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CacheFullRemoveType<String>, Serializable

    public class RemoveTypeFileSmall
extends Object
implements CacheFullRemoveType<String>
    Remove type when cache is full, data type of cache is string, and it represents the path of a file.
    • if file is smaller, remove it first
    • if file is equal to each other, remove the one which is used less
    • if file is equal to each other and used count is equal, remove the one which is first in
    Author:
    Trinea 2011-12-26
